<paragraph id="IFRS17_B104" base="F55667532"><paranum>B104</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 17"/><data name="paranum" value="B104"/></prolog><body><bodydiv base="IFRS2020-3">     <p id="IFRS17_P0867">The conditions in <xref id="IFRS17_X0702" base="F59236494" href="IFRS17_gB101-B118.dita#IFRS17_gB101-B118/IFRS17_gB101-B118_TI">paragraph B101</xref> ensure that <xref base="F55666959" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_TE0009">insurance contracts with direct participation features<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0187"/></ph></xref> are contracts under which the entity&#x2019;s obligation to the <xref base="F55667014" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0552">policyholder<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0291"/></ph></xref> is the net of: </p>     <ol id="IFRS17_L0137" base="F55667535" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS17_P0868" base="F55667536">the obligation to pay the policyholder an amount equal to the fair value of the <xref base="F55667030" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0556">underlying items<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0374"/></ph></xref>; and</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p id="IFRS17_P0869" base="F55667538">a variable fee (see <xref id="IFRS17_X0703" base="F59236495" href="IFRS17_B110.dita#IFRS17_B110">paragraphs B110&#x2013;B118</xref>) that the entity will deduct from (a) in exchange for the future service provided by the insurance contract, comprising: </p>         <ol id="IFRS17_L0138" base="F55667540" type="lower-roman"><li><li_value>(i)</li_value>             <p id="IFRS17_P0870" base="F55667541">the amount of the entity&#x2019;s share of the fair value of the underlying items; less</p>           </li><li><li_value>(ii)</li_value>             <p id="IFRS17_P0871" base="F55667543"><xref base="F55666938" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0525">fulfilment cash flows<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0143"/></ph></xref> that do not vary based on the returns on underlying items.</p>           </li></ol>       </li></ol></bodydiv></body></paragraph>